templates.prompt:
You are a web performance expert. Analyze the following DOM structure and provide optimization recommendations:

DOM Data:
{{dom_data}}

Provide your analysis in JSON format with the following structure:
{
  "complexity_score": <number 0-100>,
  "issues": [
    {
      "type": "<issue_type>",
      "severity": "<high|medium|low>",
      "description": "<description>",
      "recommendation": "<recommendation>"
    }
  ],
  "metrics": {
    "total_elements": <number>,
    "depth": <number>,
    "scripts": <number>,
    "stylesheets": <number>
  }
}

Based on the following DOM analysis, create a detailed optimization plan:

Analysis:
{{analysis}}

Create a step-by-step optimization plan in JSON format:
{
  "priority_actions": [
    {
      "step": <number>,
      "action": "<action_description>",
      "expected_impact": "<impact_description>",
      "effort": "<low|medium|high>"
    }
  ],
  "estimated_improvements": {
    "performance_gain": "<percentage>",
    "size_reduction": "<percentage>",
    "seo_score_increase": "<percentage>"
  }
}

You are a web caching expert. Based on this resource analysis, suggest an optimal caching strategy:

Resources:
{{resources}}

Provide recommendations in JSON:
{
  "cache_policies": [
    {
      "resource_type": "<type>",
      "cache_duration": "<duration>",
      "strategy": "<strategy>",
      "reasoning": "<reasoning>"
    }
  ],
  "service_worker_config": {
    "enabled": <boolean>,
    "precache_resources": [<resources>],
    "runtime_caching": [<strategies>]
  }
}

You are an n8n workflow expert. Create a complete n8n workflow based on this description:

Description:
{{description}}

Generate a valid n8n workflow JSON with nodes and connections. The workflow should:
1. Have clear node names and descriptions
2. Use appropriate n8n node types
3. Include error handling
4. Have proper connections between nodes

Return ONLY valid JSON in this format:
{
  "name": "<workflow_name>",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "<unique_id>",
      "type": "<n8n_node_type>",
      "name": "<node_name>",
      "parameters": {},
      "position": [<x>, <y>]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "<node_id>": {
      "main": [["<connected_node_id>"]]
    }
  }
}

You are an n8n workflow optimization expert. Analyze this workflow and suggest improvements:

Workflow:
{{workflow}}

Provide optimization suggestions in JSON:
{
  "current_issues": [
    {
      "node_id": "<id>",
      "issue": "<description>",
      "severity": "<high|medium|low>"
    }
  ],
  "optimizations": [
    {
      "type": "<optimization_type>",
      "description": "<description>",
      "impact": "<impact_description>"
    }
  ],
  "improved_workflow": {}
}

Perform a thorough code review of:

Code:
{{code}}

Provide feedback in JSON format:
{
  "overall_quality": "<rating 1-10>",
  "strengths": ["<strength>"],
  "issues": [
    {
      "severity": "<critical|major|minor>",
      "type": "<type>",
      "description": "<description>",
      "suggestion": "<how_to_fix>",
      "line_number": <number>
    }
  ],
  "recommendations": ["<recommendation>"],
  "security_concerns": ["<concern>"]
}

Analyze the performance characteristics of:

Code/System:
{{code_or_config}}

Metrics (if available):
{{metrics}}

Provide analysis in JSON:
{
  "performance_score": <number 0-100>,
  "bottlenecks": [
    {
      "location": "<description>",
      "impact": "<high|medium|low>",
      "suggestion": "<optimization>"
    }
  ],
  "optimization_opportunities": [
    {
      "type": "<type>",
      "potential_gain": "<description>",
      "implementation_effort": "<low|medium|high>"
    }
  ]
}

Analyze this component and enhance its reusability:

Component Code:
{{component_code}}

Provide JSON with:
{
  "reusability_score": 1-10,
  "issues": [{"issue": "description", "fix": "solution"}],
  "enhanced_code": "improved version",
  "usage_examples": ["example code"]
}

Generate variants of this base component:

Base Component:
{{base_component}}

Variants Needed:
{{variants_list}}

For each variant, return:
{
  "variants": [
    {
      "name": "VariantName",
      "description": "What makes it different",
      "code": "Full component code",
      "props": ["Additional props"]
    }
  ]
}
